      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Pedro Castro</b>\n</p><p><b>Pedro Castro Elgarresta</b>, <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><br />\na Spanish electrical engineer who graduated from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_the_Basque_Country\">University of the Basque Country</a> in 1993 <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\nAs computer chess programmer, Pedro Castro is author of the <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a> compatible <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess engine</a> <a href=\"/DanaSah\" title=\"DanaSah\">DanaSah</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>, and the <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a> compliant chess engine <a href=\"/Caligula_PC\" title=\"Caligula PC\">Caligula</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>. \nHe further hosts the <i>Hispanic Chess Engines</i> site to promote the chess engines of <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hispanic_American\">Hispanic American</a> authors, using the <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">Winboard</a> and <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> protocols <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>, also giving explanations of chess programming aspects, such as <a href=\"/Move_Generation\" title=\"Move Generation\">move generation</a>, <a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">evaluation</a> and <a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">search</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pedro_Castro&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pedro_Castro&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=3004&amp;p=14559\">depthnull</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pedro Castro</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Programming Forum</a>, July 04, 2005&#160;» <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=435719\">DanaSah 1.0 - GM Mario Gómez (1-2)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pedro Castro</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 08, 2005</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=436603\">DanaSah 1.6 vs Pablo Ignacio Restrepo (Father)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pedro Castro</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 13, 2005</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?p=32935\">danasah for linux</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pedro Castro</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, March 18, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/Linux\" title=\"Linux\">Linux</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=49221\">Caligula 0.3</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pedro Castro</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, May 29, 2008</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=49240\">Update DanaSah and Caligula</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pedro Castro</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, June 04, 2008</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pedro_Castro&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59905\">Chess on Android</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pedro Castro</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 19, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Chess_for_Android\" title=\"Chess for Android\">Chess for Android</a>, <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=65454\">Loading opening book and tablebases (xboard vs uci)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pedro Castro</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 15, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a>, <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=65977\">Relation between Nawito 1.1d and DanaSah 5.07</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pedro Castro</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 11, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=70050\">xiphos 64 bit random number</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pedro Castro</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 28, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Xiphos\" title=\"Xiphos\">Xiphos</a>, <a href=\"/Pseudorandom_Number_Generator\" title=\"Pseudorandom Number Generator\">Pseudorandom Number Generator</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=70226\">create log on android</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pedro Castro</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 17, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Android\" title=\"Android\">Android</a>, <a href=\"/Logging\" title=\"Logging\">Logging</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pedro_Castro&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/hispanicchessengines/Home\">Hispanic Chess Engines</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pedro Castro</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/hispanicchessengines/programs--interface---engines/engine\">Engine - Hispanic Chess Engines</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pedro Castro</a></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/pedro-castro-elgarresta-42911164/\">Pedro Castro Elgarresta | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pedro.castroelgarresta\">Pedro Castro Elgarresta | Facebook</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/person.php?id=647\">Pedro Castro's ICGA Tournaments</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/danasah/english/home\">Chess Engine DanaSah</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://pedrox.wixsite.com/caligula\">Caligula</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pedro_Castro&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"